I have a string defined as follows:

"""AVL LIST OF APTS High End 4bhk @ STEESHA Mount Mary Bandra Higher Floor Avl Approx 2500 sqft carpet 2 parkings Full Sea Facing Quote : Rs 30 Cr Spacious 3bhk @ PALACIO 16th Rd Bandra West Brand New Bldng Higher floor Approx 1700 sqft carpet 2 parkings Quote : Rs 9.25 Cr"""

I need to train rnn tokenizer to tokenize sentences as

Would you please help me in solving problem I'm really stucked.
